### Retrieve all users
GET {{base-url}}:30001/users
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Retrieve one user detail
GET {{base-url}}:30001/users/{{user-id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Retrieve all categories
GET {{base-url}}:30003/catalog-service/catalogs

